      "signature": "MEUCIQDf9M5o8iD0r8JmPj8Y4h2vQ2J6Q3dJgS1vPqK0xY8xVAIgX3k8L2mQ9yN6vB4wH7tD5eJ1nP8zQ2aM6yR9uW3vX0Y=",
      "keyId": "trust-root-2026-01",
      "algorithm": "Ed25519"
    }
  ]
}